name: CenterFire\u2014Bringing Music Gaming to Life! (Canceled)
blurb: A break through music game for smart phones and tablets.  Musical DNA's patented technology makes music-playing video games REAL!

rewards.reward: CRYSTAL Founders' Class: You will receive our sincerest gratitude in a Thank You Email; as well as your own Musical DNA ID which will continue to give you access to future benefits as a member of the Musical DNA Universe! You can select ONE song to be added to the CenterFire library (pending licensing). [CenterFire's additional content entry will be prioritized by the list generated by our backers.] You will also have your name visibly posted, if you choose, in our game's Production Credits\u2014via a link on the game's 'About' screen.

AMBER Founders' Class:  You'll receive a Lenticular (Holographic) Musical DNA Founder's Card, personalized with your name, founders' class and your own Musical DNA ID which will continue to give you access to future benefits as a member of the Musical DNA Universe! You'll also receive these Crystal rewards: a thank you email, ONE song of your choice added to the CenterFire library (pending licensing) and recognition in our game's production credits.

AMETHYST Founders' Class: You'll receive a Musical DNA T-Shirt with your choice of available designs and colors. You'll also receive these Moonstone rewards: a thank you email; recognition in our game's production credits; your choice of THREE songs to add to the CenterFire library (pending licensing); a limited edition Musical DNA Window Cling Graphic; and, a Lenticular (Holographic) Musical DNA Founder's Card, personalized with your name, founders' class, and your Musical DNA ID which will continue to give you access to future benefits as a member of the Musical DNA Universe!

Special Music Promotions Reward!!! AGATE Founders' Class: You will receive a 4GB USB Drive MDNA Business Card, beautifully printed on both sides and pre-loaded with an original, professionally recorded album\u2014created by two members of the Musical DNA family: Tevlin Schuetz and Corey Hall! Their new album, 'The Right & Left Outs', is an AUDIBLE CORNUCOPIA of FUNKY, ARTISTIC GOODNESS! Recorded with an incredible mix of vintage synths and other analog instruments, this music (created by just two people!!!) will simply leave you stunned. Good music deserves to be shared; be one of the first to discover some truly incredible talent! You'll also receive these Moonstone rewards: a thank you email; recognition in our game's production credits; your choice of THREE songs to add to the CenterFire library (pending licensing); a limited edition Musical DNA Window Cling Graphic; and, a Lenticular (Holographic) Musical DNA Founder's Card, personalized with your name, founders' class, and your Musical DNA ID which will continue to give you access to future benefits as a member of the Musical DNA Universe!

ONYX Founder's Class: You'll receive a Musical DNA hooded sweatshirt with your choice of available designs and colors. You'll also receive these Moonstone rewards: a thank you email; recognition in our game's production credits; your choice of THREE songs to add to the CenterFire library (pending licensing); a limited edition Musical DNA Window Cling Graphic; and, a Lenticular (Holographic) Musical DNA Founder's Card, personalized with your name, founders' class, and your Musical DNA ID which will continue to give you access to future benefits as a member of the Musical DNA Universe!

TURQUOISE Founder's Class: You will receive your choice of available designs and colors of a pair of limited edition Musical DNA UNDERWEAR or PANTIES (or even a THONG!) These custom designs will feature a choice of any of the basic Musical DNA Shapes: including Happy, Sad, Scary, Dreamy, or Funky! (Funky? ... HMMM....) You will also receive a small, limited edition, lenticular (holographic) piece of Musical DNA artwork! And, of course, you'll also receive these Moonstone+ rewards: a thank you email; recognition in our game's production credits; your choice of FIVE songs to add to the CenterFire library (pending licensing); a limited edition Musical DNA Window Cling Graphic; and, a Lenticular (Holographic) Musical DNA Founder's Card, personalized with your name, founders' class, and your Musical DNA ID which will continue to give you access to future benefits as a member of the Musical DNA Universe!

FIERY OPAL Founder's Class: You will receive a digital, e-Book version of Musical DNA Software's "Master Key of Music\u2014the Foundation\u2014for Piano". This book breaks the musical language into its most efficient, mathematical, formula\u2014providing a groundbreaking introduction to the world of music and to Musical DNA! (This would be a great gift for any true musician.) You will also receive these Agate and Turquoise rewards: a thank you email; recognition in our game's production credits; your choice of FIVE songs to add to the CenterFire library (pending licensing); a limited edition Musical DNA Window Cling Graphic; a small, limited edition, lenticular (holographic) piece of Musical DNA artwork; a 4GB USB Drive MDNA Business Card, beautifully printed on both sides and pre-loaded with an original, professionally recorded album\u2014created by two members of the Musical DNA family: Tevlin Schuetz and Corey Hall; and, a Lenticular (Holographic) Musical DNA Founder's Card, personalized with your name, founders' class, and your Musical DNA ID which will continue to give you access to future benefits as a member of the Musical DNA Universe!
